<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>NodeTrip - Discover Amazing Travel Stories</title>
    <link href="/output.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <link href="/main.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@400;500;600;700;800&family=Playfair+Display:wght@400;500;600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
</head>

<body class="min-h-screen">
    <%- include('nav.ejs', {isAuthenticated: isAuthenticated}) %>

    <!-- Hero Section -->
    <section class="pt-32 pb-16 px-4">
        <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto text-center">
            <h1 class="text-5xl md:text-7xl font-bold mb-6">
                <span class="text-gradient-primary font-serif">Discover</span> 
                <span class="text-gray-800">Amazing</span>
                <br>
                <span class="text-gradient-secondary font-serif">Travel Stories</span>
            </h1>
            <p class="text-xl text-gray-600 mb-8 max-w-2xl mx-auto leading-relaxed">
                Explore breathtaking destinations through the eyes of fellow travelers. Share your adventures and inspire others to create unforgettable memories.
            </p>
            <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 justify-center">
                <a href="/list/1" class="btn-gradient text-lg px-8 py-4">Explore Stories</a>
                <a href="/write" class="px-8 py-4 rounded-xl border-2 border-purple-500 text-purple-600 font-semibold hover:bg-purple-50 transition-all duration-300">Share Your Story</a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Filter Tabs -->
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 mb-12">
        <div class="glass-effect rounded-2xl p-2 inline-flex mx-auto">
            <button class="px-6 py-3 rounded-xl bg-white bg-opacity-80 text-purple-600 font-semibold shadow-sm transition-all duration-300">Recent</button>
            <button class="px-6 py-3 rounded-xl text-gray-600 hover:bg-white hover:bg-opacity-50 font-semibold transition-all duration-300">Most Liked</button>
            <button class="px-6 py-3 rounded-xl text-gray-600 hover:bg-white hover:bg-opacity-50 font-semibold transition-all duration-300">Trending</button>
        </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Featured Stories Grid -->
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4">
        <section class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-8 mb-16">
            <% for (let i = 0; i < 6; i++) { %>
                <article class="card-modern group cursor-pointer">
                    <div class="relative overflow-hidden rounded-t-2xl">
                        <img src="/images/image.png" alt="Travel destination" class="w-full h-64 object-cover group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform duration-700">
                        <div class="absolute top-4 left-4">
                            <span class="glass-effect px-3 py-1 rounded-full text-sm font-medium text-gray-700">Adventure</span>
                        </div>
                        <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-t from-black/20 to-transparent opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity duration-300"></div>
                    </div>

                    <div class="p-6">
                        <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-4">
                            <img src="/images/profile.svg" alt="Author" class="w-8 h-8 rounded-full">
                            <div>
                                <p class="font-medium text-gray-800">Travel Explorer</p>
                                <p class="text-sm text-gray-500">2024년 10월 15일</p>
                            </div>
                        </div>

                        <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-800 mb-3 group-hover:text-purple-600 transition-colors duration-300">
                            <%= i % 2 === 0 ? '숨겨진 보석 같은 제주도 여행지 BEST 7' : '유럽 배낭여행 2주 완벽 가이드' %>
                        </h2>

                        <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4 leading-relaxed">
                            <%= i % 2 === 0 ? 
                                '관광객들이 모르는 제주도의 숨겨진 명소들을 소개합니다. 현지인만 아는 특별한 장소에서 만든 잊을 수 없는 추억들을 공유합니다.' : 
                                '처음 유럽 여행을 계획하는 분들을 위한 완벽한 가이드입니다. 예산부터 루트까지 실전 경험을 바탕으로 한 꿀팁들을 정리했습니다.' 
                            %>
                        </p>

                        <div class="flex items-center justify-between pt-4 border-t border-gray-100">
                            <div class="flex items-center gap-4">
                                <span class="flex items-center gap-1 text-gray-500">
                                    <svg class="w-4 h-4" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                                        <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M3.172 5.172a4 4 0 015.656 0L10 6.343l1.172-1.171a4 4 0 115.656 5.656L10 17.657l-6.828-6.829a4 4 0 010-5.656z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
                                    </svg>
                                    <%= Math.floor(Math.random() * 50) + 10 %>
                                </span>
                                <span class="flex items-center gap-1 text-gray-500">
                                    <svg class="w-4 h-4" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                                        <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M7 8h10m0 0V6a2 2 0 00-2-2H9a2 2 0 00-2 2v2m10 0v10a2 2 0 01-2 2H9a2 2 0 01-2-2V8m10 0H7"></path>
                                    </svg>
                                    <%= Math.floor(Math.random() * 20) + 5 %>
                                </span>
                            </div>
                            <span class="text-sm font-medium text-purple-600">5분 읽기</span>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </article>
            <% } %>
        </section>

        <!-- Load More Button -->
        <div class="text-center mb-16">
            <button class="btn-gradient text-lg px-8 py-4">Load More Stories</button>
        </div>
    </div>
        <script src="/main.js"></script>

</body>

</html>